item.description: Regular Fit – a classic fit with good room for movement and a gently shaped waist for a comfortable, tailored silhouette.
item.content:encoded: Short-sleeved shirt in linen with a resort collar. Buttons without a placket, yoke at back, and open chest pocket. Short slits at sides and straight-cut hem.
